  THERMAL REGION (MF2)                                            6440 1451
                                                                  6440 1451
  Author: S.F, Mughabghab August 2011 (BNL)                       6440 1451
                                                                  6440 1451
  Detailed analysis of  energy-dependent capture and total cross  6440 1451
  section measurements, as well as integral thermal capture       6440 1451
  cross section measurements, revealed that the 2200 m/s          6440 1451
  thermal capture cross section is 253000-+930 b (Ref. 1).        6440 1451
   This value is consistent with the                              6440 1451
  Atlas value, 254000-+830 b (Ref. 2), the ENDF/B.VII.0           6440 1451
  thermal capture cross section and the                           6440 1451
  ICSBEP benchmarks, but is in disagreement with the RPI          6440 1451
  result(Ref.3), which is smaller by 11% than that of             6440 1451
  ENDF/B.VII.0 and the Atlas values (Ref.3).                      6440 1451
                                                                  6440 1451
