 RESONANCE REGION (MF 2)                                          6440 1451
                                                                  6440 1451
 Author:  S.F. Mughabghab August, 2011 (BNL)                      6440 1451
                                                                  6440 1451
 The parameters for resonances in MF 2 are based on the analysis  6440 1451
 presented in Ref.2. However, the parameters of the 0.0314 eV     6440 1451
 resonance were slightly altered to reflect the detailed analysis 6440 1451
 carried out in Ref. 1. These parameters are consistent with those6440 1451
 reported by Moller et al. (Ref. 4) but not those of Ref.3.       6440 1451
                                                                  6440 1451
  What can be  fully emphasized here is that the parameters of the6440 1451
  resonance at 0.0314 ev are consistent with the 2200 m/s capture 6440 1451
  cross section, derived from a host of measurements. No capture  6440 1451
  background or negative energy resonances are necessary          6440 1451
  to invoke in order to achieve consistency between the two.      6440 1451
